<span id="freeTextContainer7964040751880669715">One of the best books I’ve read this year. Such a beautiful, sad, tender, powerful story. I saw the film years ago but forgot even the broad strokes of what happens, so it was really a new story to me. It’s so well paced and easy to read. But most important of all, the characters claimed my heart — and that’s as cheesy as I’m going to get in 2021.</span>

